Dokter ajaib,

00:27:14.310 --> 00:27:14.860
kamu sudah bangun!

00:27:17.720 --> 00:27:18.180
Silakan duduk.

00:27:29.960 --> 00:27:31.090
Lukamu parah.

00:27:31.960 --> 00:27:32.700
Jangan bergerak.

00:27:33.270 --> 00:27:34.180
